item.title: CVE-2023-1835|2024-08-02T06:05:26.714Z -- unknown -- ninja%20forms%20contact%20form
item.description: The Ninja Forms Contact Form WordPress plugin before 3.6.22 does not properly escape user input before outputting it back in an admin page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
